urrent adoption.\n+\n+## Verdict Rationale\n+\n+This iteration found an active P1 finding, so the canonical iteration verdict is conditional.\n+\n+Review verdict: CONDITIONAL\n","additions":36,"deletions":0},{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-1/iterations/iteration-004.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-1/iterations/iteration-004.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-1/iterations/iteration-004.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-1/iterations/iteration-004.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/review/lineages/gpt-1/iterations/iteration-004.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,22 @@\n+# Iteration 004 - Maintainability\n+\n+Focus: phase-parent hygiene and stale relocation claims.\n+\n+Files reviewed:\n+\n+- `.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/spec.md`\n+- `.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/context-index.md`\n+- `.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/010-mcp-to-cli-tool-transition/spec.md`\n+- `.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/010-mcp-to-cli-tool-transition/004-release-and-program-cleanup/implementation-summary.md`\n+\n+## Findings\n+\n+No new findings.\n+\n+This pass replayed P2-001 and kept it at P2. The stale 028 wording is confusing and should be cleaned up, but the current parent and context index provide enough evidence to resolve th